OL,3,CRoyal family to gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FThe royal family will come together on
OL,7,FSaturday to celebrate the wedding of
OL,8,Fthe Princess Royal's son Peter
OL,9,FPhillips.
OL,11,FThe King and Queen, the Prince and
OL,12,FPrincess of Wales, Zara and Mike
OL,13,FTindall and the Duke and Duchess of
OL,14,FEdinburgh are among those expected to
OL,15,Fdescend on the small village of
OL,16,FKemble, near Cirencester in
OL,17,FGloucestershire, for the private
OL,18,Fnuptials.
OL,20,FThe Duke and Duchess of Sussex will
OL,21,Fnot attend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
