OL,3,CRoyal family to gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FIt is not known whether an invitation
OL,7,Fwas extended to Mr Phillips's cousin
OL,8,FHarry, Meghan and their children, amid
OL,9,Freports the Sussexes were left off the
OL,10,Fguest list.
OL,12,FHarry and Mr Phillips were close when
OL,13,Fyounger but it is reported they have
OL,14,Flost touch, with the duke, who has a
OL,15,Flongstanding rift with his brother
OL,16,FWilliam, moving to the US, from where
OL,17,Fhe has criticised members of his
OL,18,Ffamily and the royal institution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
