OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780783874
OL,3,CRoyal family to gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FThe late Queen Elizabeth II's eldest
OL,7,Fgrandson will tie the knot with NHS
OL,8,Fnurse Harriet Sperling in a ceremony
OL,9,Fat All Saints Church.
OL,11,FAlso expected to be there are Mr
OL,12,FPhillips's children Savannah, 15, and
OL,13,F14-year-old Isla, as well as Ms
OL,14,FSperling's teenage daughter Georgina.
OL,16,FMr Phillips's half-sister Stephanie,
OL,17,Fwho was a bridesmaid at his first
OL,18,Fwedding, is also reported to be
OL,19,Fjoining the congregation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
