OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780783874
OL,3,CRoyal family to gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FAll Saints Church, with its tall
OL,7,Fspire, sits in the heart of Kemble,
OL,8,Fwith its congregation described as
OL,9,F"very much involved in village life".
OL,11,FMr Phillips lives nearby on his
OL,12,Fmother's Gatcombe Park estate in
OL,13,FMinchinhampton.
OL,15,FThe 48-year-old is the King's nephew,
OL,16,FWilliam and Harry's first cousin, the
OL,17,Fbrother of Zara, and the son of Anne
OL,18,Fand her first husband Captain Mark
OL,19,FPhillips.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
