PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780783874
OL,3,CRoyal family to gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FMr Phillips split from his first wife
OL,7,FAutumn in 2020 after 12 years of
OL,8,Fmarriage and shares custody of their
OL,9,Ftwo children.
OL,11,FThe pair married in a grand royal
OL,12,Fwedding in St George's Chapel, Windsor
OL,13,FCastle, in 2008.
OL,15,FMr Phillips's engagement to Ms
OL,16,FSperling, who he began dating in 2024,
OL,17,Fwas announced in August last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
