PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780783874
OL,3,CRoyal family to gather in Cotswold
OL,4,Cvillage for wedding of Peter Phillips
OL,6,FThe couple were guests of Charles and
OL,7,FCamilla at Royal Ascot in June, and
OL,8,Finvited to take part in the
OL,9,Ftraditional carriage procession the
OL,10,Froyal family make on to the famous
OL,11,FBerkshire racecourse to signal the
OL,12,Fstart of the day.
OL,14,FThe wedding falls on the same day as
OL,15,Fthe Epsom Derby, with the King and
OL,16,FQueen set to dash from the ceremony to
OL,17,Fthe racecourse, ready to watch the
OL,18,Fhighlight of the racing season and
OL,19,Fpresent the trophy to the winner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
